    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/b90fbecedcd77f4ae6a79d54d3b1fd30.avif?t=1756482490\" width=932 height=236 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/07f0e4412c945bd939eacde4624fd339.poster.avif?t=1756482490\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/07f0e4412c945bd939eacde4624fd339.webm?t=1756482490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/07f0e4412c945bd939eacde4624fd339.mp4?t=1756482490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/27a75e17ad5520ad77938c3d7d2ed7ad.avif?t=1756482490\" width=932 height=236 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">As you begin your work, disturbing events unfold, revealing the Eye Order’s true nature. You discover a hidden <strong>rebellion</strong> within the facility, led by those who seek to <i>overthrow Hexcor</i>, the ruthless leader of the organization. Drawn into the conflict, you must navigate the terrifying corridors of the Order, using stealth and wits to survive, and aid the resistance in their fight to bring down Hexcor’s <i>oppressive regime.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/aca8b526d1b1a2b27abc2ad3765cc6e1.poster.avif?t=1756482490\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/aca8b526d1b1a2b27abc2ad3765cc6e1.webm?t=1756482490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/aca8b526d1b1a2b27abc2ad3765cc6e1.mp4?t=1756482490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/b0170c088b0ddbc5daf8b752f4922127.avif?t=1756482490\" width=932 height=236 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In <i>Playtown Genesis</i>, you’ll need to use <strong>stealth</strong> and <strong>clever thinking</strong> to move through the eerie corridors of the <i>Eye Order</i> without getting caught by its watchful guards. As Doctor Clint, you'll uncover dark secrets hidden deep within the facility, but trust no one. Every step is risky, and a wrong move could bring <i>Hexcor</i>'s brutal enforcers down on you. To stay safe, you'll need to crouch to avoid making noise, sneak past enemies, and work with Garnet, a key ally in the <strong>rebellion</strong>, on dangerous missions to take down the regime. <i>Outsmart enemies</i>, gather crucial information, and help the resistance bring down the oppressive order from the inside.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/697b971ab8c356fc48fb6f7bd457d046.poster.avif?t=1756482490\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/697b971ab8c356fc48fb6f7bd457d046.webm?t=1756482490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247150/extras/697b971ab8c356fc48fb6f7bd457d046.mp4?t=1756482490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
